# Per-project context

Create one subdirectory per project:

    memory/projects/<project-slug>/
        context.md       # what this project is, who's involved, status
        architecture.md  # technical shape (read on demand)
        decisions.md     # key decisions and their rationale (ADR-lite)

These files are NOT auto-loaded — read them when the agent enters a session
focused on that project. Keep MEMORY.md and ACTIVE.md for cross-project facts.
